#

Slow-Roasted Turkey with Thyme and Sage

270 min
$60
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 10

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

ThanksgivingComfort FoodMain Course

Description

A tender, juicy turkey infused with aromatic herbs for a deliciously comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • whole turkey: 12-14 pounds
  • salt: 2 tablespoons
  • black pepper: 1 tablespoon
  • fresh thyme leaves: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh sage leaves: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1/4 cup
  • garlic cloves, minced: 4
  • onion, quartered: 1
  • carrots, chopped: 2
  • celery stalks, chopped: 2
  • chicken broth: 2 cups
